name: Neil Breen
description:
Neil Breen, maker of the greatest legitimate, full-length, theatrical feature films such as Fateful Findings and I am Here.... Now

See samples for suggested prompts (especially negatives- next version of this will not be so desert prone).

Keyword is NeilBreen, and he likes to appear with CFG anywhere from 6-11 depending on the model. Trained on SD 1.5 w no VAE.
